{
  "script_id": "improper-integral",
  "voice": "zh-CN-XiaoxiaoNeural",
  "voice_key": "xiaoxiao",
  "files": [
    {
      "script_id": "improper-integral",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-1",
      "filename": "intro-intro-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/improper-integral/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.05,
      "size": 32832,
      "text": "普通的定积分，算的是一段有限区间下曲线围出的面积。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "improper-integral",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-2",
      "filename": "intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/improper-integral/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.89,
      "size": 30240,
      "text": "可如果区间一直延伸到无穷远，这块面积还有意义吗？"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "improper-integral",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-3",
      "filename": "intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/improper-integral/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.16,
      "size": 18576,
      "text": "这就是反常积分要回答的问题。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "improper-integral",
      "section_id": "infinite",
      "line_id": "inf-1",
      "filename": "infinite-inf-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/improper-integral/xiaoxiao/infinite-inf-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.2,
      "size": 35136,
      "text": "第一类反常积分，积分区间是无穷的，比如从一到正无穷。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "improper-integral",
      "section_id": "infinite",
      "line_id": "inf-2",
      "filename": "infinite-inf-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/improper-integral/xiaoxiao/infinite-inf-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.32,
      "size": 37152,
      "text": "我们先积到一个很大的上限 T，再让 T 趋于无穷，看面积的极限。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "improper-integral",
      "section_id": "infinite",
      "line_id": "inf-3",
      "filename": "infinite-inf-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/improper-integral/xiaoxiao/infinite-inf-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.94,
      "size": 31104,
      "text": "如果极限是一个有限数，就说积分收敛；否则发散。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "improper-integral",
      "section_id": "converge",
      "line_id": "con-1",
      "filename": "converge-con-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/improper-integral/xiaoxiao/converge-con-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.4,
      "size": 38448,
      "text": "看一比 x 平方，随着上限增大，面积越来越接近一，这是收敛。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "improper-integral",
      "section_id": "converge",
      "line_id": "con-2",
      "filename": "converge-con-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/improper-integral/xiaoxiao/converge-con-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.35,
      "size": 37584,
      "text": "再看一比 x，面积却随对数无限增长，永不封顶，这是发散。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "improper-integral",
      "section_id": "converge",
      "line_id": "con-3",
      "filename": "converge-con-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/improper-integral/xiaoxiao/converge-con-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.96,
      "size": 31392,
      "text": "同样铺向无穷远，两条曲线下的面积命运截然不同。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "improper-integral",
      "section_id": "unbounded",
      "line_id": "unb-1",
      "filename": "unbounded-unb-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/improper-integral/xiaoxiao/unbounded-unb-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.21,
      "size": 35280,
      "text": "第二类反常积分，区间有限，但函数在端点冲向无穷。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "improper-integral",
      "section_id": "unbounded",
      "line_id": "unb-2",
      "filename": "unbounded-unb-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/improper-integral/xiaoxiao/unbounded-unb-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.29,
      "size": 36720,
      "text": "同样用极限处理：让积分逼近那个奇点，再看结果是否有限。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "improper-integral",
      "section_id": "unbounded",
      "line_id": "unb-3",
      "filename": "unbounded-unb-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/improper-integral/xiaoxiao/unbounded-unb-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.93,
      "size": 30816,
      "text": "衰减得够快，无限高的尖峰下也能围出有限面积。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "improper-integral",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-1",
      "filename": "interaction-int-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/improper-integral/xiaoxiao/interaction-int-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.88,
      "size": 30096,
      "text": "拖动滑块增大上限 T，观察阴影面积如何变化。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "improper-integral",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-2",
      "filename": "interaction-int-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/improper-integral/xiaoxiao/interaction-int-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.85,
      "size": 29664,
      "text": "收敛的曲线面积渐渐停住，发散的却一路攀升。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "improper-integral",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-1",
      "filename": "summary-sum-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/improper-integral/xiaoxiao/summary-sum-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.37,
      "size": 37872,
      "text": "反常积分用极限，把面积的概念延伸到无穷区间和无界函数。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "improper-integral",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-2",
      "filename": "summary-sum-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/improper-integral/xiaoxiao/summary-sum-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.3,
      "size": 20880,
      "text": "极限存在就收敛，不存在就发散。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "improper-integral",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-3",
      "filename": "summary-sum-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/improper-integral/xiaoxiao/summary-sum-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.87,
      "size": 29952,
      "text": "无限的区域也可能藏着有限的面积，我们下次再见！"
    }
  ],
